.TH SLACCEPTCONNECTIONIPV4SOCKET 3 "2026-05-19" "silverlib v1.4.1" "silverlib manual"
.SH NAME
SLAcceptConnectionIPv4Socket - Accepts incoming connections
.SH LIBRARY
silverlib library
.SH SYNOPSIS
.nf
.B #define SILVER_LIB_IMPLEMENTATION
.B #include "silverlib.h"

.BI "int SLAcceptConnectionIPv4Socket(ConnectionAcceptionContext" " *ctx" ")"
.fi
.SH DESCRIPTION
Function wrapper of \fBaccept\fP(3) when any connection
is accepted, it stores the remote peer socket and address
into the \fBConnectionAcceptionContext\fP struct provided
as argument\.
.SH RETURN VALUE
Upon successful completion shall return a value of 0\.
Otherwise shall return a value of -1\.
